Y2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzA2MjEmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607=
f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd85a054e" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemsco=
pe" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impor=
tant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom=
-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> traditional fuzzy margining</a> of=
 traditional finance. FTX, Sam Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s crypto exchange, was=
 a big proponent of this, and we <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/31860043.264406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9u=
L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDYtMDEvY3J5cHRvLWNsZWFyaW5nLWFuZC1jcmVkaXQ_Y21waWQ9QkJ=
