0; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-botto=
m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> tal=
ked a lot</a> about =E2=80=9Ctokenomics,=E2=80=9D the idea of giving people=
 who use a system (say, a crypto exchange) some financial stake in the syst=
em (say, a token that gives them a share of the exchange=E2=80=99s fee inco=
me). This has some securities-law problems, and some Ponzi-ish elements, an=
d <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31860043.264406/=
aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTEtMDkvYmF=
