GVhcmluZy1zeXN0ZW0tYXQtMTY4bS1jb3N0Lw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf4a834e7" it=
emprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"col=
or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">quietly dropped them</a>.=C2=A0</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile traditional finance is like =E2=80=
=9Cugh, fine, we=E2=80=99ll do crypto, but in a normal way.=E2=80=9D Bloomb=
erg News <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31860043.=
264406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDYtMjAv=
Y3J5cHRvLWV4Y2hhbmdlLWJhY2tlZC1ieS1jaXRhZGVsLXNlY3VyaXRpZXMtZmlkZWxpdHktZ29=
