4b8524a319a23cB377b670d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" tar=
get=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; b=
order-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style:=
 solid; background-color: #ccc;">Wall Street Journal adds</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">EDX says its approach draws on standard practi=
ces in traditional, regulated financial markets and differs in key ways fro=
m how crypto exchanges typically operate.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One major difference: EDX is a =E2=80=9Cnoncus=
todial=E2=80=9D exchange, meaning it doesn=E2=80=99t directly handle its cu=
stomers=E2=80=99 digital assets. Instead, EDX runs a marketplace where firm=
s agree to execute trades of coins and dollars, using its platform to agree=
 on prices. Then the firms move crypto and cash between each other to settl=
e the trades. Later this year, EDX plans to launch a clearinghouse to facil=
itate the process of settling trades, but even then it plans to use third-p=
arty banks and a crypto custodian to hold customer assets. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Unlike most crypto exchanges, EDX won=E2=80=99=
t directly serve individual investors. Instead, it expects that retail brok=
erages will send investors=E2=80=99 orders to buy and sell digital coins to=
 its marketplace.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The stock market operates under a similar mode=
l, in which investors don=E2=80=99t directly access the New York Stock Exch=
ange or Nasdaq, but instead submit orders through brokerages such as Fideli=
ty and Schwab. =E2=80=A6</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">An institutional-only exchange in which retail=
 orders are intermediated by brokers,<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#f=
ootnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; borde=
r-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: non=
e !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-blo=
ck;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a> clearing and custody that are separate from the exchange, listing only=
 non-security tokens, no hype about blockchain. This is a way to trade cryp=
to=C2=A0while almost completely rejecting the crypto financial system. This=
 is bringing the structure of traditional finance to the assets of crypto f=
inance. Traditional finance learned nothing from the crypto financial syste=
m except that it didn=E2=80=99t work. Which is a useful lesson.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere at the Journal, <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31860043.264406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLm=
