1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">Telis Demos writes about</a> BlackRock Inc.=E2=80=99s proposed=
 Bitcoin exchange-traded fund, which we <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/31860043.264406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vc=
GluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDYtMTYvZG9uLXQtaW5zaWRlci10cmFkZS1kcnVuay1vbi10=
aGUtc3F1YXNoLWNvdXJ0P2NtcGlkPUJCRDA2MjEyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1=
haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDYyMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW=
9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB2f403824" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" item=
scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> discussed the othe=
r day</a>, and which seems to be good for Bitcoin prices. He writes:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">BlackRock=E2=80=99s application ha=
s at least one notable addition=E2=80=94an expected agreement to share =E2=
=80=9Csurveillance=E2=80=9D of a spot bitcoin-trading platform with Nasdaq,=
 which would list the ETF, according to a regulatory filing. In other words=
, the exchange could get confidential information on buyers, sellers and pr=
ices.=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Nobody quite trusts crypto exchanges to catch =
market manipulation, so they=E2=80=99ll ask Nasdaq to look for market manip=
ulation on the crypto exchanges.</p>
