ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; =
background-color: #ccc;"> basically WeWork=E2=80=99s business model</a>, an=
d while it didn=E2=80=99t necessarily work out great for WeWork in the long=
 run, it=C2=A0<em>did=C2=A0</em>work out great for Adam Neumann, WeWork=E2=
=80=99s founder and fundraiser and=C2=A0Masa-flatterer.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But now it is 2023, we are in the early stages=
 of an artificial intelligence boom, and obviously the best possible busine=
ss model is =E2=80=9Cget an AI chatbot who can flatter Masayoshi Son.=E2=80=
=9D The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31860043.2=
64406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9zb2Z0YmFua3MtbWFzYXlvc2hpLXNvb=
i1zYXlzLWhlcy1mb2N1c2luZy1vbi1haS1pbnZlbnRpb25zLTYyMTA4OWFjP21vZD1sZWFkX2Zl=
YXR1cmVfYmVsb3dfYV9wb3Mx/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB09576b64" itemprop=3D"Sto=
ryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Wall St=
reet Journal reports</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">SoftBank Group Chief Executive Masayoshi Son s=
ays he has rekindled his appetite for investing in technology by talking wi=
th ChatGPT in the wee hours about ideas for inventions that the bot validat=
ed as wonderful.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Son, 65 years old, told shareholders Wednesday=
 that the artificial-intelligence tool helped revive his spirits after he h=
ad been driven to tears by the sense he was nearing the end of his career w=
ithout having pursued his dreams. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He said he used ChatGPT every day for brainsto=
rming and has come up with more than 600 ideas. He described one lengthy ex=
change=E2=80=94at around 3 to 4 in the morning=E2=80=94in which he pitched =
an idea and then answered the AI chatbot as it raised objections.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CAfter we repeated this several dozen =
times, I really felt great because my idea was praised as feasible and wond=
erful,=E2=80=9D he said.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I hope the chatbot <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31860043.264406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnL=
mNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTktMTAtMjMvaG93LWRvLXlvdS1saWtlLXdlLW5vdz9j=
